---
---

<div class="md:max-w-4xl md:ml-auto">
  <div class="text-center md:text-left mb-14">
    <span class="eyebrow">Curriculum</span>
    <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
      What you will master
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
      We start at beginner fundamentals, then build toward real team execution:
      writing solid code and operating inside modern dev workflows.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">&lt;/&gt;</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Engineering fundamentals</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Write maintainable code with clean structure, naming, and logic.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">git</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Git and pull requests</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Branch safely, open clear PRs, and merge confidently after feedback.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">▶</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Sprint execution</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Break down tasks, report progress, and deliver in iterative cycles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">T</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Testing and debugging</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Find root causes fast, validate fixes, and avoid fragile releases.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">AI</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">AI with judgment</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Use AI and search to move faster while keeping quality and ownership.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-6">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent)]/10 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/25 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] text-sm">PR</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Career readiness</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm copy-muted leading-relaxed">
        Build proof-of-skill output you can discuss in interviews and onboarding.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
